What you need to know:  There have been numerous reports of deaths of gold miners inside tunnels, blamed on improper mining equipment Locals are still holding on to mining, which has caused a lot of pain to many, with little to show for itSome mining sites attract miners from major towns in the county, including Lodwar, Kakuma, Lokichoggio, Lokichar, and KainukCounty Director of Environment Clement Nadio says there is massive environmental degradation as a result of degraded mines